<br>
Standard Archery hits are in the high 90's, low 100's.   Crits are similar.   Crippling blows run in the 250-340 range and DO stun.   Having said all that, archery for warriors in the regular game, vs. mobs kind of blows.   There's no double attack, once you're out of arrows it's over, fletching gets quite expensive, and working up archery/fletching is a pain, although fletching is an easy ass tradeskill to master.<br>
<br>
I regularly bow kite dark blue mobs while soloing though when I get low on health (if snared first with VP Snare Spear, it's pretty awesome).  <br>
<br>
